@scotttovey "Speak the truth and shame the devil" - I'm trying to save my soul (not that I'm overly religious). Delusions are being served on mass media every day , hour , minut and second. Facts are facts and when I have a personal opinion (or idea , suggestion) about something , I always emphasize that is only my opinion. Parroting main narrative (mostly political), doesn't help anyone (quite the opposite). 
 Planetary cycles , also known as Milankovich's cycles are well known for about a century. There are other factors , regarding the climate change (some known and understood and some unknown) , but these are basic instigators of changes. Humans still don't quite understand how our planet works , in detail (there are hypotheses and I'm not an expert by no means) and yet , many people spread  "the climate religion".  Sad part is , that anyone can find many facts and information about it even on YT , never mind the serious scientific findings and discussions. 
 But , shame on me , I , sometimes , get triggered by "CO2 reduction warriors" , because they don't quite grasp , that the ultimate solution for reducing CO2 , may include getting rid of humans , which are producing CO2 , simply by being alive and breathing . Never mind the occasional barbecue .
